{"tid":1537744,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[香城online]大家千祈打爆怪物嘅私家車！","createTime":"2019-09-04T04:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T04:45:44.000Z","uid":287845,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"1a4b6ecd64b593563bd165137f9758ead49dc665","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:38:10.000Z","msg":"點解壞咗咁多閘機 都淨係得一單麻包袋?<br />\n<br />\n因為要麻包袋一隻狗，需要大量踩點&amp;事前功夫，先可以解決一隻識得逃跑識得還擊嘅狗；相反，因為個閘機唔識郁、唔識反抗、爆完就走得，所以爆狗鐵變成勇武嘅主流。<br />\n<br />\n既然勇武已經完全有刑事毀壞嘅準備，點解我地唔用同樣嘅方式制裁狗官同狗察？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">我地要嘅係車牌啊！</span><br />\n<br />\n只要有好似<span style=\"color: red;\">防假校巴bot</span>咁嘅程式，等勇武可以輕鬆check到邊啲係狗車，就唔怕誤傷無辜<br />\n<br />\n至於大家點用老鼠膠/其他工具做嘢，就自由發揮喇<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命<br />\n<br />\n利申：以上內容純屬遊戲攻略，如有雷同實屬巧合"},{"pid":"a664cac4033daf452a23f8b027dad93be80d38bf","tid":1537744,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:38:18.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月7日 (六) 1PM<br />\n機場交通壓力測試 (重考)</strong></div><br />\n<br />\n香港市民：<br />\n✅ 以遊客身份入機場觀賞飛機升降 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 唔識路就坐多幾轉車 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n✅ 必需繳付車資乘坐黨鐵<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n烏克蘭, 法國等其他國藉居民：<br />\n各有各做, 自由發揮, 唔割但要小心 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n另外可參考唔揸春袋揸輸精管方法: <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n [行動post] 肯入黎睇9.7點樣揸機場輸精管未 | LIHKG <br />\n <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1535579/page/1</a> <br />\n <br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nyixFQQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnyixFQQ.png&h=cc1f24a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>9月8日 (日) 2PM<br />\n香港人權與民主法案集會<br />\n美國駐港澳總領事館</strong></div><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2GKH20p.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2GKH20p.png&h=6178433f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d42a429054e8cba4d46db16370b962dbe6aaf669","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:38:48.000Z","msg":"自推十連"},{"pid":"d0a5feab83a1189416d74129bd04ba3f4e4c7076","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:39:01.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"3eff7214054489a45e6cb207fa2d66a28053d67a","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:39:12.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"a18edc0ec4e5be5f7f06a15c60c12673c8519f4a","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:39:22.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"a6ea83d297c8a22c5e58b38aa12c5185b5415c2f","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"fb3b6e8bd5a92be5251990149c861c4fcfc2c106","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:39:43.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"61aef699562663938723d55583d0ac661ef9ecc6","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:39:53.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"1e927792c26d8cb9e6905d574f1c3121944fed69","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:40:07.000Z","msg":"7"},{"pid":"94e8476fbeb9187355c7069b33b03f14076abee8","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:40:18.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"fd2d95ac66362de996c2ba7dcaf12e858c07584a","tid":1537744,"uid":287845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T04:40